詹姆斯·卡梅隆（James Cameron）确认，“阿凡达：火与灰”将是系列最长的电影， https://www.nme.com/news/film/avatar-fire-and-and-will-be-be-the-franceiss-long---------------------------------cameron-comeron-confirms-3844866？ m_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = avatar-fire-and-ash-will-will-be-Franchise the-the-the-the-the-filmest-film-yet-james-james-james-cameron-confirnsSurej Singh Mon, 10 Mar 2025 06:02:17 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3844866 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “&#39;水的方式&#39;正在像子弹列车一样移动，我们没有足够的角色钻探”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avatar-fire-and-ash-will-be-the-franchises-longest-film-yet-james-cameron-confirms-3844866">詹姆斯·卡梅隆（James Cameron）确认，《阿凡达：火与灰烬》将成为特许经营最长的电影</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/james-cameron-avatar@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>如果您认为<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avatar"><em>阿凡达</em></a>及其<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avatar-the-way-of-water"><em>续集</em></a>很长，请为<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avatar-fire-and-ash"><em>火和灰烬</em></a>做好准备。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/avatar-the-way-of-water-review-3366050">“化身：水的方式”评论：大胆，美丽，非常非常蓝</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据特许经营的创作者和导演詹姆斯·卡梅伦（James Cameron）的说法， <em>《火与阿什》</em>将成为迄今为止《<em>阿凡达</em>三部曲》中最长的电影，但这是一个很好的理由。在上下文中，最初的2009年<em>阿凡达</em>电影跑了两个小时42分钟，而2022年的<em>水</em>跑了三个小时12分钟。</p><p>卡梅伦（Cameron）最近在<a href="https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/avatar-fire-ash-writers-split-film-way-of-water-exclusive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《帝国》（Empire Magazine）</em></a>上发表讲话时分享说，<em>水的方式</em>“太多了好主意”，这些想法需要被分成两部电影。 </p><figure id="attachment_3840627" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3840627" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3840627" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/avatar-james-cameron@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/avatar-james-cameron@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/avatar-james-cameron@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/avatar-james-cameron@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/avatar-james-cameron@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/avatar-james-cameron@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/avatar-james-cameron@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3840627" class="wp-caption-text"> “化身”导演詹姆斯·卡梅隆（James Cameron）。学分：Ian West/PA图像通过盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>卡梅伦解释说：“简而言之，我们有太多的好主意，这是[<em>水的方式</em>]。回想起来，<em>水的方式</em>就像是子弹列车一样，我们的性格还不够。所以我说：“伙计们，我们必须分开它。” [<em>火和灰烬</em>]实际上比[<em>水的方式</em>]要长一些。”</p><p>在<em>水</em>与<em>火和灰烬</em>方面的合着者阿曼达·西尔弗（Amanda Silver）补充说，电影角色只会受益于使他们的角色弧在两部电影中发展出来：“呼吸所需的角色。这些电影不仅仅是推进的情节和华丽的奇观。我的意思是，这些是真实的角色。”</p><p><em>阿凡达：火与灰</em>将于12月19日释放。</p><p>上个月，卡梅伦似乎证实了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avatar-fire-and-ash-will-reportedly-include-anti-ai-disclaimer-3840626">即将上映的电影将以反对免责声明的形式上映</a>：“这部电影的制作中没有使用生成性AI”。詹姆斯·卡梅隆（James Cameron）对AI的厌恶不应该让人感到惊讶，就像<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/guillermo-del-toro-on-ai-it-can-do-semi-compelling-screensavers-and-thats-that-3796123">2023年7月的电影制片人反对这项技术</a>，当被问及他对AI在娱乐行业中的兴起的看法时，他指的是他的科幻经典<em>终结者</em>：“我在1984年警告过你们，而你们不听。” </p><figure id="attachment_3366054" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3366054" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3366054" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Avatar_Way_Of_Water.jpg" alt="头像" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Avatar_Way_Of_Water.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Avatar_Way_Of_Water-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Avatar_Way_Of_Water-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Avatar_Way_Of_Water-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Avatar_Way_Of_Water-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Avatar_Way_Of_Water-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3366054" class="wp-caption-text"> “头像：水的方​​式”。学分：迪士尼/20世纪工作室</figcaption></figure><p>卡梅伦补充说，他不相信AI背后的技术将能够取代作家说：“这不是谁写的问题，这是一个问题，这是一个好故事吗？”</p><p>在其他地方，詹姆斯·卡梅隆（James Cameron）最近确认，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michelle-yeoh">米歇尔·约（Michelle Yeoh）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-cameron-confirms-michelle-yeoh-will-not-be-in-avatar-fire-and-ash-3783550">不会出演电影，但她将出现在续集中</a>。 Yeoh于2019年首次宣布加入<em>Avatar</em>系列。卡梅伦（Cameron）此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-cameron-shot-avatar-3-and-4-early-to-avoid-stranger-things-ageing-issues-3370601">透露，他提前在系列中拍摄了第三部和第四部电影的场景，</a>以避免与<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/stranger-things"><em>年轻的演员</em></a>与年轻演员的衰老相关。他此前还透露，如果<em>水的方式</em>不是票房的成功，他就<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-cameron-says-he-could-end-avatar-franchise-early-if-sequel-doesnt-do-well-3345278">准备在第三部电影结束后结束特许经营</a>。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avatar-fire-and-ash-will-reportedly-include-anti-ai-disclaimer-3840626"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avatar-fire-and-ash-james-cameron-warns-fans-it-might-not-be-what-they-signed-up-for-3830548"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>阿里·塞勒（Ali Shutler）在《阿凡达（Avatar）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/avatar-the-way-of-water-review-3366050">四星级评论</a>： <em>NME</em>的<em>水之路》</em>中写道：“比原始的<em>《阿凡达》（Avatar）更大，大，更大，更好，水的方式</em>推动了电影院的技术界限，而不会像科学实验一样。确实需要在最大的屏幕上通过一对尴尬的3D眼镜看到它。不过，与前任不同，您不会急忙忘记这种经历。”</p></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avatar-fire-and-ash-will-be-the-franchises-longest-film-yet-james-cameron-confirms-3844866">詹姆斯·卡梅隆（James Cameron）确认，《阿凡达：火与灰烬》将成为特许经营最长的电影</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ;
