th="2000" height="1240" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lady-Gaga-is-seen-signing-autographs.-Credit-Getty-Images_MEGA_GC-Images-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3844382" class="wp-caption-text">看到Lady Gaga签名。信用 -  Getty Images/Mega/GC图像</figcaption></figure><p>奥尔特加（Ortega）谈到她与加加（Gaga）合作的经验：“这是最好的。她是最好的，绝对是我与之合作过的最有才华的人之一。与她和蒂姆[伯顿]在一起是一个非常非常特别的环境，我尊重的两个人受到了很多启发。”</p><p> “然后发现她是一个如此的甜心，真的很友善和保留，这很奇怪。我爱你永远不知道她会对她的期望，但是你总是可以期待仁慈和慷慨。”奥尔特加继续说道。</p><p>围绕Lady Gaga在<em>周三</em>第二季中角色的细节目前正在保存下。 </p><figure id="attachment_3830907" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830907" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830907" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830907" class="wp-caption-text">嘎嘎小姐。学分：杰夫·克拉维兹（Jeff Kravitz）/电影杂志</figcaption></figure><p>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lady-gaga-mayhem-review-3844395">“混乱”的四星级评论</a>中，尼克·莱文（Nick Levine）为<em>NME</em>写道：“&#39;Mayhem&#39;感觉就像是一张很棒的Gaga专辑，因为它非常有趣。有时，这有点像与一个老朋友重新建立联系，即使他们似乎在聊天时也有意义。当她唱着<i>“我眼中的河流，我的喉咙里有一首诗”</i>时，这只是她夸张的方式，说她很难过。 Lady Gaga在打破“ Just Dance”的十七年后，仍然是流行音乐无可挑剔的混乱特工。”</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/wednesday-review-netflix-addams-family-3353922"><em>周三</em>的四星级评论</a>中，亚历克斯·弗莱德（Alex Flood）为<em>NME</em>写道：“不管遇到困难的关系，<em>周三</em>最终都取得了罕见的衍生成功故事。这是令人毛骨悚然的，怪异的，神秘的和怪异的 - 绝对的享受。”</p><p>詹娜·奥尔特加（Jenna Ortega）邮报（Jenna Ortega <a href="https://www.nme.com">）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jenna-ortega-hails-lady-gaga-as-one-of-the-most-talented-individuals-after-working-together-on-wednesday-season-two-3844859">在“星期三”第二季一起工作后，将Lady Gaga称为“最有才华的人之一”</a> 。</p> ;
